    • Pho / Vietnamese Soup

      Our Home style pho broth is made from scratch by simmering beef bone together with star anise, onion, ginger, Saigon cinnamon and clove for 24 hours to bring out the deep flavor of beef and amazing aromas of all the ingredients.

      All pho serve with Noodles , Bean Sprout, Onion, Scallions, Lime, Cilantro, Jalapeno, Hoisin sauce and Sriracha sauce.
